race.description: G J Gardner Homes Country Boosted Showcase
race.comment: BREAKAWAY WEEK (5) won impressively first-up and has held that form since, stepping out to the mile last start at the Sapphire Coast. May have found that a bridge too far and back to this trip today is perfect with her good mate Teaghan Martin on board. Needs some luck from the draw but her best form stacks up. TILLMAN (8) has had one blip in a string of placings. He's well into the preparation, but is going well enough to get some of the money. KEN'KER (3) has been racing over a mile and hasn't been finishing off. He can go better today, and Collett is a positive jockey engagement. FIRE AND GEMSTONE (4) wont be far away in a race that looks to have a rather long tail.
